{"type": "article", "id": 16021, "title": "英伦范儿的切尔西靴又要流行，这里推荐 10 个单品", "description": "它也曾经是披头士成员热衷穿着的经典单品。", "date": "2015-10-14T06:05:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 5619, "name": "流行趋势"}, {"id": 17152, "name": "切尔西靴"}], "category": 19, "author": 75588, "comment_count": 14, "praise_count": 339, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607104459tzfciC9u6r8GWhZ0.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t虽说运动鞋的流行依然没有减弱，但据说今年秋冬切尔西靴又要回来了。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t切尔西靴（<span>Chelsea boot</span>）最早可以追溯到英国维多利亚时代，当时不论男女都穿<span>切尔西靴。但以现在的眼光来看，<span>切尔西靴则被认为是</span>在 </span>20 世纪 60 年代英国的标志性元素——当时 MOD 文化中的典型打扮——它也曾经是披头士成员热衷穿着的经典单品。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104454UnMbIlwEKrDo1Cxp.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66574074\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t鉴于<span>切尔西靴没有明显的性别之分，无非就是跟部高低，其余部分的结构几乎没有任何变化性，只能在面料、纹路、鞋跟纹路上花心思。说实话，这种差异跟条纹 Tee、白衬衫之类单品的差异一样微妙。鞋头尖一点或者圆一点，觉得鞋底软或者硬，脚背高或者低人各不同，最好是亲自试过。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>至于搭配，它似乎是超级百搭的优雅单品。除了过于活泼的街头装扮之外，任何裤型和外套 hold 住都没问题。顺便说一句，姑娘们也完全可以一试，利落，有活力。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>这里有十双我们觉得还不错的，喜欢的话请自行去各大海淘网站捞取。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104455Kyw805eDURHLlN1n.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.71771429\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<span>Saint Laurent </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104455hAqyRwKJIlX87tzH.jpg\" title=\"Ps by Paul Smith\" alt=\"Ps by Paul Smith\" data-ratio=\"0.71771429\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>Ps by Paul Smith</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104456kpJgudySOBAH2RvE.jpg\" title=\"Berluti\" alt=\"Berluti\" data-ratio=\"0.71771429\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>Berluti</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606071044567dyfiUKXcWGMB925.jpg\" title=\"R.M. Williams\" alt=\"R.M. Williams\" data-ratio=\"0.71771429\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>R.M. Williams</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104457Cnjoe4lXYhgM0iaU.jpg\" title=\"Dr. Martens\" alt=\"Dr. Martens\" data-ratio=\"0.71771429\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>Dr. Martens</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104457ajNdWCHU69fyvXgi.jpg\" title=\"Maison Martin Margiela\" alt=\"Maison Martin Margiela\" data-ratio=\"1.06625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>Maison Martin Margiela</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104458nf6cegOoaUALilH8.jpg\" title=\"Aquatalia\" alt=\"Aquatalia\" data-ratio=\"0.71771429\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>Aquatalia</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104458uNlEj6BHzOsekoJn.jpg\" title=\"Grenson\" alt=\"Grenson\" data-ratio=\"0.71771429\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>Grenson</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606071044594Z0KhoLlcNtHRxjC.jpg\" title=\"Common Projects\" alt=\"Common Projects\" data-ratio=\"0.71771429\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>Common Projects</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104459f3YGFNZmiK1j9Dpb.jpg\" title=\"A.P.C.\" alt=\"A.P.C.\" data-ratio=\"0.71771429\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>A.P.C.</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}